## Additional Information About The Code Snippets Above :





The first model (`MinPool2D`) utilizes a minimum pooling layer followed immediately By another maxpooling operation, aiming at extracting features from an Input Tensor 'X'. While Max Pooling has been shown effective In image classification tasks,, employing Minimum poolin offers advantages such as reducing overfitting compared To conventional Maximum POOLING techniques.`​﻿ ​This technique finds applications where minimizing variance rather Than maximizing it yields better results.​ Additionally，the second Model ('FC') incorporates various layers including Convolutional Layers ("DW" And "Pw"), Batch Normalization("BN") alongside MAX AND MIN Pools For feature extraction purposes.''

